  • public class Plank
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a plank (edge) between two pillars (vertexes) in the temple grid used in the DocJones algorithm
    Author:
    Harry Nelken (hrn10@case.edu) For EECS 293 - Vincenzo Liberatore Software Craftsmanship
